01:40:24.159 --> 01:40:30.182
So, if that's you, we'll send you an Amplified Bible, a New King James, or a King James—whatever.

01:40:30.183 --> 01:40:37.945
But we just want to love on you and tell you, 'Welcome home. Welcome to the family.'So, get plugged into your local church.

01:40:37.946 --> 01:40:43.999
Don't go to a dead church. Go to a live church. I'd go to a non-denominational Holy Ghost filled church.

01:40:44.000 --> 01:40:48.399
You don't want to go to some dead church because there's a lot of them out there.

01:40:48.400 --> 01:40:56.079
Get plugged into a radical church that believes in the baptism of the Holy Ghost and speaking in tongues.

01:40:56.080 --> 01:40:59.165
Find some new friends. If you have to, invite your old friends to come to church.

01:40:59.166 --> 01:41:07.919
Say, 'Listen, will you come with me to church?'They say, 'No, we're not into religion stuff.'It's not about religion; it's about relationship.

01:41:07.920 --> 01:41:16.439
And the more you get close to Jesus, they're going to say, 'What is different about you?'because He will change you from the inside out.

01:41:16.440 --> 01:41:24.330
The more you get this Word inside of you, He will change you from the inside out. You've got to read this Bible every day, though.

01:41:24.331 --> 01:41:39.879
Find words that pertain to what you're believing Him for, and you'll find scriptures and read them and go, 'Wow, this has become life to me.'So, all 29 of you that gave your heart to Jesus Christ today, welcome to the family.

01:41:39.880 --> 01:41:46.682
All 29 of you. Isn't Jesus wonderful? 29 people gave their heart to Jesus Christ today. 29.

01:41:46.683 --> 01:41:52.319
So, welcome home, welcome back, whatever it may be, if you're rededicating or whatever.

01:41:52.320 --> 01:41:59.976
The Lord said, 'Give an altar call.'That's interesting. 29 people gave their hearts to Jesus Christ, so that's wonderful.

01:41:59.977 --> 01:42:04.179
You all have big plans today—go out and eat hot dogs or do anything fun.

01:42:04.180 --> 01:42:09.058
Are you going to pop fireworks? Go watch fireworks or something here in America. It's so fun.

01:42:09.059 --> 01:42:19.359
The Nathan's Hot Dog Eating Contest is this afternoon, and we always watch that to see Joey Chestnut eat as many hot dogs as he can.

01:42:19.360 --> 01:42:24.638
75 is his record, I think. So, we'll watch Joey Chestnut eat if he's still there.

01:42:24.639 --> 01:42:33.359
But he eats so many hot dogs; I don't even know how he does it. In less than 10 minutes, 75 hot dogs in his belly.

01:42:33.360 --> 01:43:15.199
My goodness, I have to eat mine real slow. 76—he did 76. For those who are led by the Spirit of God are the sons and daughters of God.

01:43:15.200 --> 01:43:21.519
So He will lead you with that still, small voice on the inside of you. You need to know that.

01:43:21.520 --> 01:43:28.498
So if He tells you not to do something, follow His leading because it could be life and death for you.

01:43:28.499 --> 01:43:35.039
If you have a strong caution—'Don't go here, don't go there'—follow it.

01:43:35.040 --> 01:43:42.106
Follow that peace that passes all understanding today. Let peace be your umpire.

01:43:42.107 --> 01:43:48.849
Follow peace and you will not be led astray. God is the Prince of Peace.

01:43:48.850 --> 01:43:55.319
Jesus is the Prince of Peace, and He will lead you with that still, small voice of that peace that passes all understanding.

01:43:55.320 --> 01:44:00.513
Follow it. The Holy Spirit and I believe those led by the Spirit of God are the sons of God, daughters of God.

01:44:00.514 --> 01:44:06.399
And you don't need prophetic voices to tell you what's coming; you hear the voice of the Spirit of the Lord yourself.

01:44:06.400 --> 01:44:13.759
But He brings people like us around to help pray. And I believe that's what my assignment is: to pray for the nations.

01:44:13.760 --> 01:44:18.238
So, God bless you all, and we're so thankful for you being here today.

01:44:18.239 --> 01:44:23.439
If you could like, subscribe, click the notification bell, click the thumbs up, and be a part of this.

01:44:23.440 --> 01:44:29.118
You can come here and pray. We're believing for 1 million men and women to come and pray with us.

01:44:29.119 --> 01:44:36.559
Pray for me, too. But pray for us and pray with us, and in doing so, we will change the nations for Jesus.

01:44:36.560 --> 01:44:46.538
We're almost to 600,000-some subscribers. So yeah, pretty cool what God has done in just three years.

01:44:46.539 --> 01:44:51.219
Remember, like I said, put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

01:44:51.220 --> 01:45:01.920
Jesus loves you and we love you. God bless you and we'll see you again. Have a wonderful and happy Fourth of July. Bye-bye.

